{"word":"ὑψόω","slug":"ὑψόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑψόω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὕψος'><el>ὕψος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to lift high, raise up</i>, <a href='S:Batrachomyomachia'>Batr.</a>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b>: <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to raise for oneself</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to elevate, exalt</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}